SET ECHO OFF
* ============================================================
* DOTTALK_BETA0_SMOKE_BASELINE_0_1.DTS
*
* Purpose:
*   Fast Beta-0 verification harness.
*
* Scope:
*   - engine bring-up
*   - workareas
*   - index/order behavior
*   - relation backend + FoxPro relation syntax
*   - tuple correctness
*   - buffered write visibility
*   - expression / predicate sanity
*
* Notes:
*   - keep this short
*   - avoid destructive operations
*   - use as a gate before larger regression runs
* ============================================================

ECHO ===== BETA-0 SMOKE START =====
COLOR DEFAULT
VERSION

ECHO ===== 1. ENGINE / PATHS =====
INIT
SET PATH
WSREPORT

ECHO ===== 2. SCHEMAS / WORKAREAS =====
SCHEMAS CLOSE
SCHEMAS OPEN DBF
SCHEMAS
SELECT STUDENTS
AREA

ECHO ===== 3. STORAGE / BASIC ROW ACCESS =====
STRUCT
FIELDS
COUNT
TOP
RECNO
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME
DISPLAY

ECHO ===== 4. ORDER / INDEX =====
SET INDEX TO students.cdx
SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
AREA
TOP
RECNO
LIST 5
SEEK TAYLOR
RECNO
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME
SET ORDER TO 0
TOP
RECNO
LIST 3

ECHO ===== 5. EXPRESSIONS / PREDICATES =====
LOCATE lname = Taylor
RECNO
BOOLEAN (GPA > 2)
BOOLEAN (GPA < 4)
CALC GPA
CALC DATE()
CALC DOB
CALC DATE() - DOB

ECHO ===== 6. RELATION BACKEND (NATIVE) =====
REL CLEAR ALL
REL ADD STUDENTS ENROLL ON SID
REL ADD ENROLL CLASSES ON CLS_ID
REL LIST
REL LIST ALL
REL REFRESH

ECHO ===== 7. RELATION BACKEND (FOXPRO SURFACE) =====
REL CLEAR ALL
SELECT STUDENTS
SET RELATION TO SID INTO ENROLL
REL LIST
SELECT ENROLL
SET RELATION TO CLS_ID INTO CLASSES
REL LIST
SELECT STUDENTS
REL LIST ALL

ECHO ===== 8. RELATION REMOVE / CLEAR =====
SELECT ENROLL
SET RELATION OFF INTO CLASSES
REL LIST
SELECT STUDENTS
SET RELATION OFF ALL
REL LIST

ECHO ===== 9. RELATION EQUIVALENCE =====
REL CLEAR ALL
REL ADD STUDENTS ENROLL ON SID
REL LIST
REL CLEAR ALL
SELECT STUDENTS
SET RELATION TO SID INTO ENROLL
REL LIST

ECHO ===== 10. TUPLE / CROSS-AREA =====
REL CLEAR ALL
REL ADD STUDENTS ENROLL ON SID
REL ADD ENROLL CLASSES ON CLS_ID
SELECT STUDENTS
LOCATE lname = Taylor
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME
REL LIST ALL

ECHO ===== 11. BUFFER VISIBILITY =====
SET INDEX TO students.cdx
SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
LOCATE lname = Taylor
LIST 1
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,GPA
TABLE ON
REPLACE FNAME WITH "DeraldBeta"
TUPLE SID,LNAME,FNAME,GPA
LIST 1
COMMIT
SEEK Taylor
LIST 1
REPLACE FNAME WITH "Derald"
COMMIT
TABLE OFF
SEEK Taylor
LIST 1

ECHO ===== 12. CALCWRITE VISIBILITY =====
LOCATE lname = Taylor
TABLE ON
TUPLE GPA
CALC GPA = GPA + 0.01
TUPLE GPA
COMMIT
SEEK Taylor
LIST 1
CALC GPA = GPA - 0.01
COMMIT
TABLE OFF
SEEK Taylor
LIST 1

ECHO ===== 13. SMARTLIST / FILTER SANITY =====
SET ORDER TO TAG LNAME
SMARTLIST 5 FOR GPA >= 3.5
SET FILTER TO LNAME = "TAYLOR"
LIST 10
SET FILTER TO

ECHO ===== 14. CLEAN SHUTDOWN =====
SET ORDER TO 0
REL CLEAR ALL
SCHEMAS CLOSE
ECHO ===== BETA-0 SMOKE END =====
QUIT